FROM [sys].[default_constraints] [d]
INNER JOIN [sys].[columns] [c] ON [d].[parent_column_id] = [c].[column_id] AND [d].[parent_object_id] = [c].[object_id]
WHERE ([d].[parent_object_id] = OBJECT_ID(N'[EstudianteMaterias]') AND [c].[name] = N'Periodo');
IF @var1 IS NOT NULL EXEC(N'ALTER TABLE [EstudianteMaterias] DROP CONSTRAINT [' + @var1 + '];');
ALTER TABLE [EstudianteMaterias] DROP COLUMN [Periodo];
